title: Ahimsa Vegan Restaurant and Club
typeOfFood: Vegan, International, Mediterranean, Fast food, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Asian, Fusion, Middle Eastern
description: Serves Middle Eastern and Far Eastern vegan fusion cuisine with dishes like falafel with Palestinian spices, hummus, sizzlers, veggie sushi, curry, thali, and dosa. Beer from small local brewers. Also houses a space for concerts. Opened by Najadacze.pl in Jun 2015.
